 role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 03, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xmo1665703396183.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xmo1665703396183.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xmo1665703396183.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xmo1665703396183\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                    \n Uniface Messages 4000-4999\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Refer to the Uniface message number, message text, and an explanation of the\n    message.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The following table refers to messages with numbering between\n        <span class=\"keyword msgnum\">4000</span>-<span class=\"keyword msgnum\">4999</span>.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__1\">Message number</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__2\">Message text</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__3\">Explanation</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword msgnum\">4100</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__2\"><samp class=\"ph msgph\">Your current Uniface repository will be migrated</samp></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__3\">You have objects in the repository that are imported from an older release. These\n              objects will be migrated to match the new repository structure.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword msgnum\">4200</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__2\"><samp class=\"ph msgph\">Uniface version information copied to message frame</samp></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__3\">When you click any of the hyperlinks on the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">About Uniface</span>\n              form (for example, Release, Update, Platform, or Date), the information for all four\n              is copied to the message frame.<p class=\"p\">You can copy and paste the information from the\n                message frame, for example, to an email to Uniface support.</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword msgnum\">4300</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__2\"><samp class=\"ph msgph\">Load License failed</samp></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__3\">Your attempt to load the OCX's runtime license failed. Make sure that you have\n              selected the OCX, and that the OCX has a runtime license.<p class=\"p\">Before you try to use\n                runtime OCX licenses, check that the OCX in use supports runtime licenses and that\n                you are allowed to use them. This should be in the documentation of the OCX\n                involved; otherwise the manufacturer of the OCX should be able to provide this\n                information.</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword msgnum\">4301</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__2\"><samp class=\"ph msgph\">Load License successful</samp></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__3\">The OCX runtime license was loaded.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword msgnum\">4302</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__2\"><samp class=\"ph msgph\">License unloaded</samp></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__3\">The OCX runtime license was unloaded.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword msgnum\">4400</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__2\"><samp class=\"ph msgph\">The IDE's state has been reset due to an update</samp></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__3\">A new version of the Uniface IDE has been installed which is incompatible with\n              the state saved in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">ide_state.zip</span> file. As a consequence, the\n              existing state is dropped and the default (compiled-in) state is used.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword msgnum\">4401</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__2\"><samp class=\"ph msgph\">The IDE's state for\n                  <var class=\"keyword varname\">ObjectType</var>:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ObjectName</var> has been reset due to\n                an update</samp></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__3\">A new version of the Uniface IDE has been installed which is incompatible with\n              the state of editor for the specified object, as saved in the\n                <span class=\"ph filepath\">ide_state.zip</span> file. As a consequence, the existing state is\n              dropped and the default (compiled-in) state is used.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword msgnum\">4800</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__2\"><samp class=\"ph msgph\">Select a date</samp></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__3\">No date was set or selected for the calendar widget. Click on a date to select\n              it.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword msgnum\">4801</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__2\"><samp class=\"ph msgph\">Date was out of range.</samp></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"xmo1665703396183__table_dpj_hxq_rwb__entry__3\">The initial value specified for the calendar date is invalid. Select or provide a\n              correct date.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533793\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533793\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Uniface Messages 4000-4999 Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 03, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Uniface Messages 4000-4999 Refer to the Uniface message number, message text, and an explanation of the message. The following table refers to messages with numbering between 4000 - 4999 . Message number Message text Explanation 4100 Your current Uniface repository will be migrated You have objects in the repository that are imported from an older release. These objects will be migrated to match the new repository structure. 4200 Uniface version information copied to message frame When you click any of the hyperlinks on the About Uniface form (for example, Release, Update, Platform, or Date), the information for all four is copied to the message frame. You can copy and paste the information from the message frame, for example, to an email to Uniface support. 4300 Load License failed Your attempt to load the OCX's runtime license failed. Make sure that you have selected the OCX, and that the OCX has a runtime license. Before you try to use runtime OCX licenses, check that the OCX in use supports runtime licenses and that you are allowed to use them. This should be in the documentation of the OCX involved; otherwise the manufacturer of the OCX should be able to provide this information. 4301 Load License successful The OCX runtime license was loaded. 4302 License unloaded The OCX runtime license was unloaded. 4400 The IDE's state has been reset due to an update A new version of the Uniface IDE has been installed which is incompatible with the state saved in the ide_state.zip file. As a consequence, the existing state is dropped and the default (compiled-in) state is used. 4401 The IDE's state for ObjectType : ObjectName has been reset due to an update A new version of the Uniface IDE has been installed which is incompatible with the state of editor for the specified object, as saved in the ide_state.zip file. As a consequence, the existing state is dropped and the default (compiled-in) state is used. 4800 Select a date No date was set or selected for the calendar widget. Click on a date to select it. 4801 Date was out of range. The initial value specified for the calendar date is invalid. Select or provide a correct date. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}